DENGUE/DHF UPDATE 2011 (32)
***************************

A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

In this update:
Reports from various countries
Asia
---
Thailand (Krabi)
Viet Nam
Philippines (Pampanga)
India (Jharkhand state)
India (Delhi)
India (Punjab state)
Caribbean
---
Turks and Caicos ex Bahamas and St. Lucia
